com.forgerock.opendj.cli

Interface ToolRefDocContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArgumentParser, ControlPanelArgumentParser, InstallDSArgumentParser, LDAPConnectionArgumentParser, ReplicationCliArgumentParser, SecureConnectionCliParser, StatusCliArgumentParser, SubCommandArgumentParser, UninstallerArgumentParser

    public interface ToolRefDocContainer
    An interface for an object that holds reference documentation for a command-line tool.
